<div class="container-fluid container-fluid-custom py-md-5 mb-5">
  <main>
    <div class="row py-md-5 text-center justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-8 mb-6 mb-md-0">
        <h1 class="display-2 fw-bold mb-4 position-relative home-title">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h1>
        
        <div class="faq-section">
          <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">1. What is NoteNest?</h3>
            <p>NoteNest is a powerful note-taking app that helps users organize and manage their notes efficiently. It allows users to create, edit, and delete notes while keeping them synced across all devices.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">2. How do I create a new note?</h3>
            <p>To create a new note, simply log in to your account, go to the Notes section, and click on the "Create New Note" button. You can then add your content and save it instantly.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">3. Can I access my notes from multiple devices?</h3>
            <p>Yes, all your notes are automatically saved and synced across all devices where you have logged in. You can access them anytime, anywhere.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">4. Is my data secure?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely! NoteNest uses encrypted storage to ensure your notes are securely stored. Only you have access to your notes through your account.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item mb-4">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">5. Can I delete a note?</h3>
            <p>Yes, if a note is no longer needed, you can delete it. Simply select the note and click on the "Delete" option. The note will be removed permanently.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Explore Notes</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
